<div class="" style="font-size:110%;"><a href="List_of_dialects_of_the_English_language" title="List of dialects of the English language">Dialects</a> and <a href="Regional_accents_of_English" title="Regional accents of English">accents</a> of <a href="Modern_English" title="Modern English">Modern English</a> by continent</div>
</th>
</tr>
